      "response_body": "<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"zh-hant\"><head><title>輕小說文庫 - 輕小說百科</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\" /><meta content=\"IE=edge\" http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" /><meta content=\"yes\" name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-capable\" /><meta content=\"輕小說文庫包括一週一次買同學的那些事～兩個人的時間，藉口的五千元～、放課後的百物語、汝為吾之騎士、異世界一擊無雙姐姐、義妹生活、怪人的沙拉碗、我的網婆是超人氣偶像 冰山美人的她在現實世界也想當我老婆、朱華姬的親衛、在謊言的世界裡，我談了一場難忘的戀愛...\" name=\"description\" /><meta content=\"telephone=no\" name=\"format-detection\" /><meta content=\"black\" media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" name=\"theme-color\" /><meta content=\"white\" media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" name=\"theme-color\" /><meta content=\"initial-scale=1,shrink-to-fit=no,width=device-width\" name=\"viewport\" /><link href=\"https://LNovel.tw/books\" hreflang=\"zh-hant\" rel=\"alternate\" /><link href=\"https://LNovel.org/books\" hreflang=\"zh-hans\" rel=\"alternate\" /><link href=\"https://LNovel.tw/books\" hreflang=\"x-default\" rel=\"alternate\" /><link href=\"/uploads/auth/app/icon/000/000/005/0ba10cca.png\" rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" /><link href=\"/uploads/auth/app/icon/000/000/005/t144_0ba10cca.png\" rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" /><link href=\"/uploads/auth/app/icon/000/000/005/ico_0ba10cca.ico\" rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/x-icon\" /><link href=\"/auth/apps/manifest.json\" rel=\"manifest\" /><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/assets/acg/novel/application-c4e1b71a6e31d12b8b482e012c2bc1a380b3d7c356ed44b05ae1c6772b2e378b.css\" media=\"all\" /><script src=\"/assets/acg/novel/application-d3f3eaa91c7c0efef722ac59b3c9f6b861f15618d806305a727ca21df1d0ad6e.js\" async=\"async\"></script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"name\":\"文庫\",\"item\":\"https://lnovel.tw/books\",\"position\":1},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"name\":\"輕小說文庫\",\"item\":\"https://lnovel.tw/books\",\"position\":2}]}</script><link href=\"/books?page=2\" rel=\"next\" /><meta name=a