/img/webpic/26/ws0720l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>異世界一擊無雙姐姐</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-2996\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/19/ymsh0212l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>義妹生活</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3464\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/8/slgr1123l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>怪人的沙拉碗</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3251\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/2/wp0517l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>我的網婆是超人氣偶像 冰山美人的她在現實世界也想當我老婆</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3853\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/21/zh0908l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>朱華姬的親衛</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3851\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/12/zhy0908l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>在謊言的世界裡，我談了一場難忘的戀愛</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3852\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/9/my0908l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>在滿月之夜找到你</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3723\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/18/mk0229l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>我要和女主角的妹控哥哥離婚</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-2093\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.muwai.com/img/webpic/15/asdxks6789l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>小書痴的下克上(愛書的下克上)</a></div><div class=\"row gx-2 gy-3 mb-3 text-center\"><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-1522\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.muwai.com/img/webpic/13/zdxcxqxhsfgclsm676l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>在地下城尋求邂逅是否搞錯了什麼(期待在地下城邂逅有錯嗎)</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3163\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/24/bq1031l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>敗北女角太多了！(敗犬女主太多了！)</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3759\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/15/ht0506l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>為何我總是成為S級美女們的話題</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3850\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/6/sn0830l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>少女星間漂流記</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3849\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/1/xn0830l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>獻給你的故事</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-1697\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.muwai.com/img/webpic/28/adydc6890l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>安達與島村</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3698\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/5/hl017l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>黑狼王與白銀人質公主～在邊境之地得到最愛～</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3504\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/26/yxdn0117l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>與幼小的你一起，將聲音傳到遠方</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3635\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/10/qp1004l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>被扔進棋盤裡</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-2559\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.muwai.com/img/webpic/18/sh1010l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>被死神撫養的少女懷抱漆黑之劍</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3766\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/6/gzqj05109l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>貴族千金，只與我親近</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-2026\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.muwai.com/img/webpic/6/ctyqx3786l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>春夏推理事件簿</a></div><div class=\"row gx-2 gy-3 mb-3 text-center\"><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3845\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/24/bn0826l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>我與她的夏日重現</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3848\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/24/yz0826l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>一週後，我會殺了你</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3847\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/19/nl0826l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>奴隸們對我充滿期待與好評，害我無法壓榨她們</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3846\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/14/mw0826l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>想要確定真命天女之前，可以先拿我試試哦。</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3423\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/12/edlz1014l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>在只有我能升級的世界成為惡德領主</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3296\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/23/zs0710l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>日常生活中不起眼的平凡大叔，其實是地表最強戰神</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3408\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/0/sm1004l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>水屬性的魔法師</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3268\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/10/ym0616l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>其實是繼妹。～總覺得剛來的繼弟很黏我～</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3222\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/28/cfyx0319l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>辣妹因為懲罰遊戲才向我這個邊緣人告白，但顯然是真心愛上我了</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-3649\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; height: 120px;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"w-100 h-100\" src=\"/uploads/https/xs.idmzj.com/img/webpic/16/hm1023l.jpg.small.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>轉生為故事的黑幕～以進化魔劍和遊戲知識傲視群倫～</a><a class=\"col-6 col-md-4 col-md-3 col-lg-6 col-xl-4\" href=\"/books-2651\"><span class=\"d-block mx-auto mb-1 bg-body-tertiary\" style=\"width: 90px; heig